문항#The human resources department director at SAL Advertising ____ Ms. Briola the senior copywrite position, because the management likes her sample work so much.
(A) made
(B) offered
(C) recruited
(D) hired
답#(B)
주석#V [Ms. Briola] [the senior copywrite position] 따라서 V는 5형식 동사가 와야 하는데, 가능한 것은 made, offered이다. 문맥 상 더 적절한 것은 offer : 제공하다
이다.

